debris injured 14 others, two of them seriously.
   The blast ignited a fire that swept through a parking garage
beneath a seven-story office building, destroying the cars, police
said. The cars' exploding gas tanks kept firefighters from entering
the garage for more than an hour.
   Police said they don't know what caused the explosion.
