<HEAD>Robbers, Police Exchange Gunfire in Bank Siege</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 5 grafs to UPDATE with standoff over, no suspects
found inside, two suspects believed at large, name of hostage officer.
O'Connel is cq. Picks up 3rd graf, `The robbers.... SUBS 7th graf, `Another
